Package de.dfki.omm.types

Various special data types used throughout the OMS.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TypedValue
    Interface for typed OMM values, such as binary coded payloads or URLs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryValue
    Implementation of TypedValue modeling binary values (such as binary coded payloads).
    CertificateIssuer
    Provides input for the issuing of a certificate via KeyStore.
    GenericTypedValue
    Implementation of TypedValue modeling any values for which no specific class exists.
    ISO8601
    Handles the ISO8601 date format and conversions from and to it.
    LinkTypes
    Contains types of links as static fields.
    OMMEntity
    An individual or agent that initiates changes in the state of an OMM.
    OMMEntityCollection
    A list of OMMEntitys.
    OMMFormat
    Describes the format of an OMM block's payload.
    OMMMultiLangText
    A map of Locales and corresponding Strings (of the specified language) for multi language support.
    OMMPreviousBlockLink
    Provides the ID and type of a previous block.
    OMMSemanticsGroup
    A Vector of OMMSemanticsInfos to collect all semantic information of a semantic block.
    OMMSemanticsInfo
    Provides semantic information for an OMMSemanticsBlock, comprising a subject, predicate, object and a time span or date for which the predicate is valid for the two units.
    OMMStructureInfo
    Provides structure information for an OMMStructureBlock, comprising a relation type, target and a time span or date for which the relationship is valid.
    OMMSubjectCollection
    A List of OMMSubjectTags to represent an OMM block's collected subjects.
    OMMSubjectTag
    A single subject tag which might be or be part of an OMM block's subject field.
    URLType
    Implementation of TypedValue specifically modeling an URL type.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OMMMetaAttribute
    Enumerator listing all metadata fields of OMM blocks.
    OMMPreviousBlockType
    Enumerator listing the known types of previous blocks.
    OMMRestAccessMode
    Enumerator listing valid access modes for the OMS REST interface.
    OMMSourceType
    Enumerator to describe the OMM's type of source from which it can be loaded when the OMS (re)starts.
    OMMStructureRelation
    Enumerator listing all known relations to be found in structures.
    OMMSubjectTagType
    Enumerator describing all known types of subject tags.

Package de.dfki.omm.types Description

Various special data types used throughout the OMS.
